{
  "name": "ListColumn",
  "summary": "<p><strong>ListColumn</strong> 对象是 <strong>ListColumns</strong> 集合的成员。<strong>ListColumns</strong> 集合包含表格中的所有列（<strong>ListObject</strong> 对象）。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>ListObject</strong> 对象的 ListColumns 属性可返回一个 <strong>ListColumns</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给活动工作簿的第一个工作表的默认 ListObject 对象添加新 ListColumn 对象。由于未指定位置，因此在最右边添加一个新列，并显示列名。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listColumn = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listColumn.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第二列删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表表格中的一列。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code>*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DataBodyRange",
      "summary": "<p>返回的对象不包含标题单元格和总计单元格。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Range</strong> 对象，该对象为列的数据部分的大小。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第二列数据单元格的数量，不包含标题单元格和总计单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBodyRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第四列单元格字体大小设为 20 磅，不包含标题单元格和总计单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBodyRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表 <strong>ListColumn</strong> 对象在 <strong>ListColumns</strong> 集合中的索引号。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第二列的索引号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第三列索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "<p>该属性值还被用作列表列的显示名称。此名称必须在列表中唯一。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表列表列的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第三列的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> objListCols = listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(objListCols.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第四列名称改为“列四”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;列四&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Range",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Range</strong>对象，它代表在以上列表中的指定列表对象所应用的区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第三列单元格的宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第一列单元格边框的粗细设置为粗线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThick\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Total",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>ListColumn</strong> 对象的总计行。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第二列总计行的值是否大于15。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Total</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">15</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第一列的总计行的地址。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Total</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "TotalsCalculation",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>XlTotalsCalculation</strong> 可为以下 <strong>XlTotalsCalculation</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationNone</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationSum</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationAverage</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationCount</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationCountNums</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationMin</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationStdDev</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationVar</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlTotalsCalculationMax</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>无须显示“总计”行即可设置此属性。此属性没有固定的“默认”值。随着对其他列的添加或删除，ET 会更改该属性的状态。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>基于 <strong>XlTotalsCalculation</strong>枚举的值，确定列表列的“总计”行中的计算类型。可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第一列总计行的计算类型设置为xlTotalsCalculationSum。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TotalsCalculation</span> = xlTotalsCalculationSum\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第四列的总计行的计算类型是否为xlTotalsCalculationAverage。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TotalsCalculation</span> == xlTotalsCalculationAverage)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlTotalsCalculation",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "XPath",
      "summary": "<p>当 <strong>XPath</strong>属性包含的区域满足以下条件时，该属性有效：  </p>\n<ul>\n<li>区域中仅有一个单元格。</li>\n<li>如果区域中包含两个或更多个单元格，那么必须满足以���条件之一：  <ol>\n<li>如果单元格包含 XPath 信息，区域内的所有单元格都必须包含 XPath 信息（也即，每个单元格与一个或多个数据映射关联），所有单元格还必须具有相同的 XPath 内容（也即，每个单元格向同一组数据映射提供数据）。  </li>\n<li>所有单元格都不包含 XPath 信息。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>区域内没有不连续的区域。  <div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>注释</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>表格的标题和总计行被视为包含 XPath 信息。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></li>\n</ul>\n<p>任何不满足上述条件的区域将返回运行时错误。</p>\n<p>如果区域选择有效，但未映射任何单元格，ET 将返回一个 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象，这样您就能通过访问 <strong>SetValue</strong>方法来创建映射。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>XPath</strong>对象，它代表映射到指定 <strong>Range</strong>对象的元素的 XPath。该区域的上下文确定操作是否成功，或返回空对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象中第一列的XPath对象的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表的第一个 ListObject 对象的第三列架构映射。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XPath",
